title: Firefox keeps randomly opening multiple new pages.
content: Firefox keeps randomly opening multiple new pages. It does not happen when I start my computer but randomly at any time it suddenly pops up new Firefox windows and then resets the page when I try and search the web. It does this to such an extent that I can't even work on the computer. I have Firefox on my devices and they are working fine.
creator: maratainhp
